{"title":"春天的味道（外一首）","authors":["杨泽远"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的味道（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨泽远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日天气心情好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走，咱们骑上自行车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到田野深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去放飞喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞欢笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们把风缀上衣襟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着炫目的野花野草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤起脚丫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与鬼灵的河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大野里所有的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都咯咯咯在笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天蓝得教你流泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云白得教你起跳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随手摘一片柳叶衔着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满嘴都是春天的味道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日天气心情好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连牛羊都忘了吃草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们索性不回家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把阳光花香夹进面包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这么一小口一小口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝尝春天的味道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一条浅绿的枝条上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都爬满了金色的蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从它身旁走过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使挨得很近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也惊不飞它，而且还能听到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘤嘤的铜质的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这声音使人想起乡间的唢呐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那么亲切，让人动情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛每一个细小的音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都包含着鲜亮的吉祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和温软的轻风"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}